    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "I'd suggest enhancing the `url_for` function to accept callables as well, i.e. the function name unquoted; as this would help e.g. with code refactoring tools and auto completion.\r\n\r\nIt can easily be implemented with a few lines; if such a functionality would be desirable, I can prepare a PR with tests, etc.\r\n\r\nBest regards, Christian",
