            "body": "@ThiefMaster gave you an argument why such behavior would be technically incorrect. You're right that this would help with tab-completion, but I don't think that's a good reason to mangle an API. If you want to use it in your own projects, that's totally fine. I don't think you need to monkeypatch anything though, because you can always just import your new `url_for` function and use that, no?"
